### Side API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5132/api/side

### Create a new side
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stationId": 1,
  "sideName": "Hash Browns",
  "sideDescription": "Crispy hash browns",
  "sidePrice": 2.99,
  "imageUrl": "https://picsum.photos/id/550/150/150"
}

### Get all sides
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get a specific side by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Update a side
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stationId": 1,
  "sideName": "Hash Browns Supreme",
  "sideDescription": "Crispy hash browns with cheese and bacon",
  "sidePrice": 3.99,
  "imageUrl": "https://picsum.photos/id/550/150/150"
}

### Delete a side
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1

### Set Side In-Stock Status
PUT http://localhost:5132/api/side/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

false